                    </div>
                    <div class="grid-our-values">
                        <div class="card connection"> <!-- Classe .connection aplicada aqui -->
                            <span class="icon-card">
                                <i class="ri-shake-hands-line"></i>
                            </span>
                            <h4>Connection</h4>
                            <p>Our focus is to make interactions between companies easy. We believe that efficient collaboration and communication are fundamental for success in the business environment. Therefore, we dedicate our efforts to creating solutions that simplify and enhance connections between our business partners, ensuring quick and effective information exchange.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card visual"> <!-- Classe .visual aplicada aqui -->
                            <span class="icon-card">
                                <i class="ri-bar-chart-grouped-line"></i>
                            </span>
                            <h4>Visual</h4>
                            <p>We focus on enabling clients to visualize transactions through intuitive and detailed graphs. We understand that good data visualization is essential for informed decision-making. Our graphs provide a clear and comprehensible view of business activities, helping our clients monitor and analyze their operations effectively.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card management"> <!-- Classe .management aplicada aqui -->
                            <span class="icon-card">
                                <i class="ri-archive-drawer-line"></i>
                            </span>
